          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-hugh-bayley" title="Mr Hugh Bayley">Hugh Bayley</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Deputy Prime Minister how many<span class="italic">(a)</span> pensioners and<span class="italic">(b)</span> other people have received help to insulate their homes in York in each year since 1997. [188947]</p>
        </blockquote>
